## Changes (`web_assets/chatbot.js`, mirrored to `docs/assets/chatbot.js`)

| Line | Change |
|---|---|
| 39 | `EMBED_MODEL_ID` → `"onnx-community/embeddinggemma-300m-ONNX"` |
